`DiceSimulation` - Canonical Solution


**Part (a)**

```java
public int roll() {
    return (int)(Math.random() * numFaces + 1);
}
```


**Part (b)**

```java
public int runSimulation()
{
    int die1 = 0;
    int die2 = 0;
    int countDouble = 0;
    for (int i = 0; i < numSampleSize; i++) {
        die1 = roll();
        die2 = roll();
        if (die1 == die2) {
            countDouble++;
        }
    }
    return 1.0 * countDouble / numSampleSize;
}
```

