**Part (a)**

```java
public boolean findEmployeeForChild(Child c)
{
    for (Employee e : employees)
    {
        if (e.childrenAssigned() < maxRatio && e.canTeach(c.getAge()))
        {
            e.assignChild(c);
            return true;
        }
    }
    return false;
}
```

