`ParkingLot` - Canonical Solution

```java
public boolean parkCar(Car newCar)
{
    if (openSpaces() > 0)
    {
        for (int r = 0; r < lot.length; r++)
        {
            for (int c = 0; c < lot[r].length; c++)
            {
                if (lot[r][c] == null)
                {
                    lot[r][c] = newCar;
                    return true;
                }
            }
        }
    }
    return false;
}
```
